name: Through Time (alpha map) v1
description:
Through Time is an indie game created by Nikola Janev. This version contains just the map which you can download and test it on your PC.

Storyline: The main character travel through time to save the world from something dark, your mission is to prevent that. In the first level, you are in medieval ages to save queen Liana and her elf sword. She is the last remaining elf.

Warning: You can experience some bugs while running this game.
